=== 巴塞罗那 ===
[[2007年至2008年西班牙甲組聯賽|2007年至2008年西班牙甲組聯賽]]，巴塞罗那只能屈居[[皇家馬德里|皇家馬德里]]及[[維拉利爾|維拉利爾]]獲得聯賽第三名，是由2002/03年賽季後首次跌出聯賽首兩名。由於根據[[歐洲足聯積分排名|歐洲足聯積分排名]]西甲聯賽冠亞軍可以直接晉身歐聯分組賽階段，季軍則需要參加第三圈預選賽階段賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.xs4all.nl/~kassiesa/bert/uefa/access2008.html |title=2008/09年賽季歐洲聯賽冠軍盃各地聯賽分配名額 |accessdate=2007-10-12 |archive-date=2007-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012203907/http://www.xs4all.nl/~kassiesa/bert/uefa/access2008.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
，因此巴塞罗那6年來首次參加第三圈預選賽<ref>{{cite news |title=Continental powers to learn fate |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=735566.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-07-31 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416121430/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=735566.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，並會遇上[[波蘭|波蘭]]聯賽冠軍－[[維斯瓦克拉科夫足球俱樂部|維斯瓦克拉科夫]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Schalke-Atlético pick of the draw |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=735569.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-08-01 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090602201857/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=735569.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，首回合在[[魯營球場|魯營球場]]以4比0大勝對手；次回合作客波蘭以1球落敗，總成績仍以4比1出線分組賽階段。<ref>{{cite news |first=Delfín |last=Ramírez |title=Brilliant Barça sweep Wisła aside |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15275/match=303817/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-08-13 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090603170231/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15275/match=303817/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Luciano |last=Mera |title=Cléber rouses Wisła but Barça pass test |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15275/match=303833/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-08-26 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604051833/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15275/match=303833/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>在分組賽階段的23支參賽球隊中，巴塞隆拿的UEFA評分為117.837分，成為第一種子的8支球隊之一<ref>{{cite news |title=Europe's finest set for group stage draw |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=740905.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-08-28 |accessdate=2009-05-23 |archive-date=2008-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828083944/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=740905.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，經過抽籤後巴塞罗那與[[瑞士|瑞士]]的[[巴素利|巴素利]]、[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]的[[薩克達|薩克達]]及[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的[[士砵亭|士砵亭]]處於同一小組。<ref>{{cite news |title=Hard work ahead for Laporta's Barça |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=743396.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-08-28 |accessdate=2009-05-23 |archive-date=2009-06-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090603170242/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=743396.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

巴塞罗那在分組賽賽事完全盡顯一支勁旅的實力，代表作包括先後作客巴素利及士砵亭分別大勝5比0及5比2，賽完第5輪分組賽賽事後已經獲得出線16強淘汰賽資格，巴塞罗那在最後一輪分組賽賽事派出全副選陣容以2比3不敗薩克達。總結巴塞罗那在6場分組賽賽事取得共18球，成為分組賽階段攻擊力最強的球隊，亦創了自2002/03年改制後分組賽最多入球的紀錄<ref>{{cite news |first=Andy |last=Brassell |title=Breathtaking Barça continue goal glut |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15276/match=302758/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-12-26 |accessdate=2009-05-23 |archive-date=2009-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090928040743/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15276/match=302758/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>巴塞罗那以小組首名出線，根據賽制無須在16強階段遇上小組次名以及同國球隊，包括[[拜仁慕尼黑|拜仁慕尼黑]]、[[曼聯|曼聯]]、[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]。<ref>{{cite news |title=Europe awaits UEFA Champions League draw |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=787334.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-12-19 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2008-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218015214/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind%3D1/newsid%3D787334.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 最終巴塞罗那在被抽中與法國7屆聯賽冠軍[[里昂足球會|里昂]]爭入8強。<ref>{{cite news |title=Holders United to take on Inter |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=788360.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-12-19 |accessdate=2009-05-23 |archive-date=2008-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081220153059/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind%3D1/newsid%3D788360.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在首回合作客[[里昂|里昂]]，開賽7分鐘里昂由[[P·祖連奴|P·祖連奴]]一個自由球為主隊先開紀錄，巴塞罗那直到上半場67分鐘由[[蒂埃里·亨利|蒂埃里·亨利]]追回1比1，這個入球不但賽和對手並且獲得[[作客入球優惠|作客入球優惠]]回到[[魯營球場|魯營球場]]。<ref>{{cite news |first=Matthew |last=Spiro |title=Henry header brings Barça reward |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15277/match=302789/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2009-02-24 |accessdate=2009-05-23 |archive-date=2009-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090502012834/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15277/match=302789/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>次回合巴塞罗那回到主場開賽迅速採取攻勢，[[蒂埃里·亨利|蒂埃里·亨利]]、[[美斯|美斯]]及[[伊度奧|伊度奧]]在上半場合共攻入4球，上半場早段里昂連入兩球，為球隊出線重現希望，不過巴塞罗那在臨完場由[[施度·基達|施度·基達]]再入一球，最終巴塞隆拿大勝里昂5比2，總比數以6比3成功晉身半準決賽階段。<ref>{{cite news |first=Graham |last=Hunter |title=First-half flurry seals Barça passage |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15277/match=302793/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2008-03-11 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090430225141/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15277/match=302793/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在半準決賽階段，巴塞罗那遇上2001年歐聯冠軍－[[德國|德國]]勁旅[[拜仁慕尼黑|拜仁慕尼黑]]，拜仁慕尼黑在16強階段總比數以12比1淘汰[[士砵亭|士砵亭]]，打破歐冠盃淘汰賽階段總比數最大差距紀錄。<ref>{{cite news |title=English teams dominate draw lineup |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=809373.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2009-03-20 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090708143751/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=809373.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="draw">{{cite news |title=Porto placed in United's path |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=811234.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2009-03-20 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905030028/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/news/kind=1/newsid=811234.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>巴塞罗那首回合主場迎戰拜仁慕尼黑，開賽早段由[[美斯|美斯]]及[[伊度奧|伊度奧]]領先2球，及後在上半場末段由[[美斯|美斯]]及[[蒂埃里·亨利|蒂埃里·亨利]]拋離至4比0，最終該比數維持至完場，巴塞罗那輕鬆擊敗對手。<ref>{{cite news |first=Graham |last=Turner |title=Barça brilliance turns tables on Bayern |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15278/match=302804/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2009-04-08 |accessdate=2009-05-22 |archive-date=2009-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090802033149/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15278/match=302804/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>接著次回合作客[[慕尼黑|慕尼黑]]，主隊拜仁慕尼黑由[[列貝利|列貝利]]於47分鐘首開紀錄，不過首回合落後4球令拜仁慕尼黑難以追回，由於沒有取得作客入球，因此必須在餘下時間攻入4球才可以出線，直到73分鐘巴塞罗那由[[基達|基達]]追回1比1，最終巴塞罗那總比數5比1擊敗拜仁慕尼黑晉身準決賽階段。<ref>{{cite news |first=Gavin |last=Jackson |title=Bayern save face as Barcelona keep apace |url=http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15278/match=302806/report=rp.html |work=uefa.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=2009-04-14 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2010-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100124190652/http://www.uefa.com/competitions/ucl/fixturesresults/round=15278/match=302806/report=rp.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

巴塞罗那在準決賽迎戰的對手是兩支[[英超|英超]]球隊[[利物浦足球會|利物浦]]及[[車路士|車路士]]其中之一。<ref name="draw"/>車路士在首回合作客以3比1擊敗利物浦，<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Liverpool 1-3 Chelsea |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7977013.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-08 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2017-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909192318/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7977013.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>車路士回到主場一度被利物浦連入兩球，之後車路士連入三球反超前，但利物浦在比賽後段再攻入兩球，最後車路士由[[林柏特|林柏特]]為主隊射成4比4，總比數以7比5出線準決賽迎戰巴塞隆拿。<ref>{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Fletcher |title=Chelsea 4-4 Liverpool (agg: 7-5) |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7977038.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-14 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090419014745/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7977038.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>準決賽首回合在[[魯營球場|魯營球場]]進行。尽管巴塞罗那掌控了大部分的控球权，但切尔西藉着裁判誤判及卓有成效的防守成功抵挡住了巴塞罗那的进攻，最终双方战成0-0，切尔西也成为了本赛季第一支没有在魯營球場失球的球队。<ref>{{cite news |first=Jonathan |last=Stevenson |title=Barcelona 0-0 Chelsea |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010833.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-28 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-05-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501173646/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010833.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 

第二回合的比赛里，巴塞罗那在开场不久就被攻破球门。[[兰帕德|兰帕德]]的传球被挡出禁区之外，[[迈克尔·埃辛|埃辛]]左脚大力抽射，球击中横梁后入网，巴塞罗那的守门员[[维克托·巴尔德斯|巴尔德斯]]对此毫无办法。在接下来的时间里，和首回合一样，巴塞罗那掌控了大部分的控球权。尽管如此，切尔西还是创造了多次有威胁的进攻。[[阿尔维斯|阿尔维斯]]领到了一张黄牌，这是他在淘汰赛阶段的第三张黄牌，根据规则他不能参加巴塞罗那的下一场欧联比赛。[[阿内尔卡|阿内尔卡]][[插水_(足球術語)|-{zh-hans:假摔;zh-hk:插水;zh-tw:假摔;}-]]让[[阿比达尔|阿比达尔]]领到了红牌，令落後的巴塞少打一人。切爾西的的攻勢在對方少打一人的情況下更加凌厲，多次在巴賽禁區內製造險情，但是都沒有再為切爾西添分。本場裁判下半场的补时为4分钟。似乎切尔西已经进入了决赛，但在第93分钟，梅西传球到禁区边缘，[[伊涅斯塔|伊涅斯塔]]射门，[[切赫|切赫]]没能碰到皮球。巴塞罗那凭借着这个客场入球进入了决赛。<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Chelsea 1-1 Barcelona (agg 1-1) |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010840.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-05-06 |accessdate=2009-05-07 |archive-date=2009-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090505235236/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010840.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>本場裁判赫寧作出多次爭議判決，除了阿比達爾的紅牌之外，還有比賽25分鐘時馬盧達在禁區被阿爾維斯犯規，赫寧卻判決是禁區外自由球、26分鐘時德羅巴在禁區被身後的阿比達爾拉倒沒有任何表示、56分鐘時德羅巴再次突入禁區被亞亞圖雷從身後放倒赫寧依舊沒有表示、81分鐘皮克禁區內張開雙手的明顯手球赫寧依舊沒表示、96分鐘巴拉克射門被高舉雙手的埃托奧擋出，也沒有判罰點球。<ref>{{cite news |first=Barney |last=Corkhill |title=The Great Debate: Chelsea Vs Barca: Did The Ref Actually Get It Right? |url=https://bleacherreport.com/articles/170680-the-great-debate-chelsea-vs-barca-did-the-ref-actually-get-it-right |work=Bleacherreporter |publisher=Bleacherreporter |date=2009-05-09 |accessdate=2009-05-09 |archive-date=2020-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107224523/https://bleacherreport.com/articles/170680-the-great-debate-chelsea-vs-barca-did-the-ref-actually-get-it-right |dead-url=no }}</ref>

