=== 曼聯 ===
上屆冠軍盟主曼聯，在分組賽進行衛冕。曼聯是頭八名的種子球隊，这意味着曼联不会在小组赛里遇到巴塞罗那、[[国际米兰|国际米兰]]和[[皇家马德里|皇家马德里]]这些前欧联冠军，但有可能遇到拜仁慕尼黑或者罗马。<ref>{{cite news |title=Man Utd to face Celtic in Europe |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7584644.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2008-08-28 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2008-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081218122205/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7584644.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

兩場勝利（作客對[[阿爾堡|阿爾堡]]及主場擊敗[[些路迪|些路迪]]）及四場平手足以使曼聯出線，在最後一輪同組的些路迪擊敗[[比利亚雷亚尔足球俱乐部|維拉里爾]]，曼聯從而取得分組冠軍晉身第三圈。<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Man Utd 2-2 Aalborg |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7763234.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2008-12-10 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2008-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081211094649/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7763234.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 在第二圈球隊可以避免面對分組冠軍[[罗马足球俱乐部|羅馬]]、巴塞隆拿、[[拜仁慕尼黑|拜仁慕尼黑]]、[[波尔图足球俱乐部|波圖]]及[[尤文圖斯足球俱樂部|祖雲達斯]]，但是曼联的对手有可能是国际米兰、[[里昂足球俱乐部|里昂]]或者皇家马德里。最后曼联和[[穆里尼奥|穆里尼奥]]的国际米兰相遇。由于曼联是小组第一，国际米兰是小组第二，所以双方第二回合的比赛在曼联的主场进行。<ref>{{cite news |title=Man Utd to face Mourinho's Inter |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7790235.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2008-12-19 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2020-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201006114927/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7790235.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在首回合的比赛里，曼联和国际米兰战成0-0。这场平局之后，曼联在欧洲冠军联赛里连续保持20场不败，打破了[[阿贾克斯|阿贾克斯]]保持了13年的连续19场不败的记录。<ref>{{cite news |first=Mark |last=Ashenden |title=Inter Milan 0-0 Man Utd |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7904057.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-02-24 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2009-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090227083207/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7904057.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref> 没能在客场进球意味着曼联必须尽量避免国际米兰在[[老特拉福德|老特拉福德]]进球。开场第4分钟，[[维迪奇|维迪奇]]头球为曼联建功。尽管[[伊布拉希莫维奇|伊布拉希莫维奇]]头球击中横梁，但国际米兰似乎难以取得进球。[[克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多|克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多]]在下半时第4分钟的进球最终为曼联锁定胜局。<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Man Utd 2-0 Inter Milan (agg 2-0) |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7899577.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-03-11 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2017-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904164426/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7899577.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

八強曼聯抽到與[[波圖足球會|波圖]]對決，兩隊曾經在[[2003–2004年歐洲冠軍聯賽|2003–04年度]]分組賽對戰。勝出的一分可與[[阿森納足球俱樂部|阿仙奴]]或維拉里爾勝方交手。<ref>{{cite news |title=Liverpool draw Chelsea in Europe |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7954390.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-03-20 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2009-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090323044517/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7954390.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>第一輪比賽在奧脫福進行，波圖在开场第4分钟射進了一球，給予曼聯壓力。10分钟后，[[鲁尼|鲁尼]]打入一球，为曼联扳平比分。在第85分钟，[[特维斯|特维斯]]的进球让曼联领先。但仅过了一分钟，曼联的后防出现了失误，波尔图抓住这个机会打入一球，将比分锁定为2-2。<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Man Utd 2-2 FC Porto |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976964.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-07 |accessdate=2009-05-09 |archive-date=2009-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090410130658/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976964.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>曼聯需要在葡萄牙作客時勝出或打和2-2或以上戰果才有機會出線。开场仅6分钟，克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多在40码外远射得分。在接下来的时间里，双方都没能取得进球。曼联也成为了第一支在波尔图的主场赢球的英国球队。<ref>{{cite news |first=Paul |last=Fletcher |title=FC Porto 0-1 Man Utd (agg 2-3) |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976970.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-15 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2009-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090421043649/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976970.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[阿森纳|阿森纳]]在客场以1-1战平维拉里尔，在主场[[酋长球场|酋长球场]]以3-0获胜，在半决赛里和曼联相遇。<ref>{{cite news |first=Jonathan |last=Stevenson |title=Villarreal 1-1 Arsenal |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976997.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-07 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2009-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416201011/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976997.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=Dawkes |title=Arsenal 3-0 Villarreal (agg 4-1) |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976998.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-15 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2009-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090417064727/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/7976998.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>首回合比赛在老特拉福德举行。鲁尼、特维斯和克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多在开场不久都获得不错的得分机会，但没能进球。接着曼联获得角球。角球传中后，阿森纳未能解围，[[卡里克|卡里克]]得球后往底线一扣接着传中，球被阿森纳的球员碰到之后反弹到[[奥谢|奥谢]]的面前，奥谢一脚射门将球打进。在接下来的时间里，曼联创造了多次进球的机会，阿森纳也获得了一些机会，但双方均未能把握。最后比分锁定为1-0，曼联带着胜利前往[[伦敦|伦敦]]。在那里只要不输球，曼联就将成为继1997年的[[尤文图斯|尤文图斯]]之后又一支进入欧洲冠军联赛决赛的卫冕冠军。<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Man Utd 1-0 Arsenal |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010847.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-04-29 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2012-06-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/689oeJGsd?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/europe/8010847.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>阿森纳希望在第二回合的主场里击败曼联，但这个希望在开场11分钟内就被[[朴智星|朴智星]]和克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多破坏了。在第8分钟，[[基兰·基比斯|基兰·基比斯]]在禁区内滑倒，朴智星抓住机会射门得分。3分钟后，克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多在41码处的大力任意球射门破网得分。阿森纳必须至少打入曼联4球才能晋级。但打入下一个进球的还是曼联的球员。阿森纳在前场丢球，曼联队抓住机会快速反击15秒内由克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多得分。15分钟后，[[弗莱彻|弗莱彻]]在禁区内对[[法布雷加斯|法布雷加斯]]的犯规不但让阿森纳获得点球机会，也让自己领到了红牌。但录像显示弗莱彻是先碰到球的。[[罗宾·范佩西|范佩西]]打入了这个点球，不過這不足以阻止曼聯晉身決賽。<ref>{{cite news |first=Phil |last=McNulty |title=Arsenal 1-3 Man Utd (agg 1-4) |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010853.stm |work=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=2009-05-05 |accessdate=2009-05-06 |archive-date=2009-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090507083346/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/europe/8010853.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

